title: Once a G.O.P. Stalwart, Liz Cheney Hits the Trail for Democrats
description: Stumping for Elissa Slotkin in Michigan, Ms. Cheney had an urgent message for voters: “We all must stand and defend the republic.”
dc:creator: Jonathan Weisman
media:description: Representatives Liz Cheney and Adam Kinzinger, both Republicans, are campaigning against supporters of former President Donald J. Trump who are seeking office.
